{
  "stem": "13313.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I found out later what-- what-- what this switch came from.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Why-- why we went to visit my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It so happens that it was the custom for the organization told with the slave labor that after three months, I understood-- I've been told afterwards was told after, that after three months of hard labor the people automatically were shipped off to Auschwitz and then new people be brought in after them.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So  they had an unlimited supply of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it was just so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father was sent on a transport to Auschwitz three months after he was taken away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that means we're talking here he was-- he was taken away probably I would say August.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Went into hiding in September.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So October, November he was on this-- on this transport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans again said we're going to relocate you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're going to go to other labor camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was just-- just to be more efficient to prevent kind of revolts and all that stuff they would tell the people it was always the good news.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But always there were-- there were rumors.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Always rumors percolating.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father was the kind of person that believed the rumors.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He believed the worst.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He didn't want to-- to put his head-- bury his head  in the sand and believe that everything was going to be OK.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the boxcar, he-- he more or less knew that they were still in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And apparently he told himself-- by the way, his brother was on the same transport, but not in the same car.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My Uncle Jacques.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they were taken together in the same transport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he looked around and there was another chap with him by the name of Joseph [?",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
